        <div class="star-item">
            <h4>Eye Contact</h4>
            <p>70% maintained, natural breaks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="star-item">
            <h4>Verb Consistency</h4>
            <p>Past tense for experiences, present for current role</p>
        </div>
        <div class="star-item">
            <h4>Smooth Transitions</h4>
            <p>Natural flow between STAR elements</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h3>Hand Gesture Guidelines</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Descriptive gestures:</strong> Show size, direction, process flow</li>
        <li><strong>Emphatic gestures:</strong> Highlight key points</li>
        <li><strong>Keep gestures within "speech box":</strong> Shoulder width, waist to chest height</li>
        <li><strong>Avoid:</strong> Pointing, fidgeting, repetitive movements</li>
    </ul>
</div>

